Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,下一级 境界触发者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大规模侵略开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,触发 启动
